      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-codebase-semantics-document:code:5:1",
      "@type": "CodeBlock",
      "labels": [
        "CodeBlock"
      ],
      "name": "Code 1",
      "chunk_text": "- [ ] Neutrality; represent codebases generically; forbid project-specific assumptions\n- [ ] Provenance; track origins and paths; forbid metadata loss\n- [ ] Determinism; canonicalize identifiers; forbid unstable IDs\n- [ ] Separation; decouple indexer from renderer; forbid cross-layer imports\n- [ ] Performance; bound traversal operations; forbid unbounded scans in UI",
